{"tid":2222240,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】留守唔係問題，但泛民一定要兌現承諾","createTime":"2020-09-29T03:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T23:41:08.000Z","uid":221035,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbeafbeb6b3b6cb840f4e83ae2b56875193c6d4","tid":2222240,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔想再糾纏咩民調問題，呢啲係政治決定，無論接受委任定杯葛，要自己承受政治後果<br />\n泛民想留，無人阻到，咁你咪留飽佢<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">不過！</span></span></strong><br />\n民主黨之前口聲聲話留低可以擋住明日大愚、可以擋住大灣區投票、又可以擋保皇啲濕9議案，唔該你真係同我擋曬佢，唔好開空頭支票，你話咗擋到，如果第時照過，我逐條同你計<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">仲有</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好再側側膊，出席率無98％唔好話自己盡咗力，講到留低咁巴閉，唔該做返出嚟<br />\n如果班泛民真係個個都慢必、朱迪上身，22個慢必咁款捱一年，我寫個服字俾你又點話<br />\n但如果泛民只係繼續開空頭支票、欺騙選民，大隻講，哈哈，以後唔洗留係政圈"},{"pid":"4c858d23081ff043ee4d2e4232c215b3224c7d49","tid":2222240,"uid":292181,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"其實留定唔留都好，咁樣互屌就中晒中共圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ab5efab5b3cde3d384f16bdd04b89f95bd106c","tid":2222240,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1ec3e60e82610e5181ff518e6e01182ee361ba","tid":2222240,"uid":72654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241d99378cc59b70025fcf5508bad5cd2d0780c8","tid":2222240,"uid":70964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"接受委任一定唔會投, 一票都不會投 完"},{"pid":"43954b68e181d9083cf72987a16aaebc3932e315","tid":2222240,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"不厭其煩提醒大家，民主黨之前講到明留低係要擋住明日大愚同埋大灣區投票，仲話要擋住好多「惡法」"},{"pid":"069c380086c440f33f39effd468bd0acd9d5d653","tid":2222240,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241d99378cc59b70025fcf5508bad5cd2d0780c8","tid":2222240,"uid":70964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"接受委任一定唔會投, 一票都不會投 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦，super，大家以後都無票投，選舉都無㗎喇"},{"pid":"a77f2ecfa94022214d4e49f46bdfa6b26334c8be","tid":2222240,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e50966886a9817103141e69ecd8c2d97813773","tid":2222240,"uid":281501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f03cbbf3e2f173503cc564e4e3668d4b570e5ec","tid":2222240,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"069c380086c440f33f39effd468bd0acd9d5d653","tid":2222240,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241d99378cc59b70025fcf5508bad5cd2d0780c8","tid":2222240,"uid":70964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"接受委任一定唔會投, 一票都不會投 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦，super，大家以後都無票投，選舉都無㗎喇"},"citedBy":0,"reply